Project Statement – AI Fitness & Health Calculator

Problem Statement
Modern students and individuals often struggle to understand basic fitness metrics such as BMI, calorie needs, and personalized workout advice. Manual calculation is time-consuming, inaccurate, and confusing. A simple automated system is needed for quick and reliable health assessment.

Scope
This project provides:
- Automated BMI calculation
- Categorization into health ranges
- Calorie estimation based on gender, age, height, weight, activity level
- Personalized fitness suggestions
- Clear input → process → output workflow

Target Users
- Students tracking fitness
- Beginners in health and gym routines
- Individuals wanting fast health evaluation
- People without access to paid apps

High-Level Features
- BMI Calculation Module
- Calorie Estimation Module
- Activity Level Integration
- Health Advice System
- Modular Python Implementation
